These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, puzzles, skydiving
City: liverpool, miami, venice, san-francisco
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, light-blue, apricot, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who likes light-blue is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the person who likes apricot is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | camping | skydiving   | photography  | puzzles  |
| City   | miami    | san-francisco    | liverpool      | venice    |
| Color   | ebony | light-blue | apricot | orange |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

