.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, october, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
There 4 different types of food: garlic, mango, apple, lettuce
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, subway, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
3. the person eating lettuce is the person driving the subway##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person eating apple and the person driving the bus##2
6. the person driving the boat is between the person watching western movies and the person eating lettuce##2
7. the person eating garlic is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | november | april    | october  | september    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Food           | lettuce      | apple       | mango      | garlic       |
| Transport         | subway    | boat | snowmobile | bus |

