.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, disaster, action, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, hip-hop, indie
There are 4 different nationalities: french, italian, russian, brazilian
1. the fan of hip-hop is the italian##1
2. the italian is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the russian is on the left of the italian##1
4. the italian is on the left of the french##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
6. the fan of metal is the person watching epic movies##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
9. the person watching action movies is between the person eating lemon and the fan of metal##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Movie-Genre       | disaster   | spy   | action | epic |
| Music-Genre         | ambient   | hip-hop | indie       | metal    |
| Nationality   | russian    | italian | french  | brazilian    |

