 7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the fan of punk and the person who's birthday is in may##2
10. the person who's birthday is in july is the fan of gospel##1

