3. the person playing scrabble is between the aristoff-smoker and the person playing bridge##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing scrabble is the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | drama       | thriller     | epic      |
| Game   | backgammon   | bridge      | scrabble   | canasta   |
| Cigar         | davidoff   | siglo    | ritmeester | aristoff   |

